---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import partyImage from "../assets/images/party.avif";
---

<section id="producto" class="bg-background py-20 sm:py-24">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <p class="font-body font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-secondary">Nuestra Edici칩n Insignia</p>
      <h2 class="font-display text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold mt-2 text-text">VOLCANIC</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="relative flex justify-center items-center">
      <div class="w-full lg:w-4/5">
        <Image
          src={partyImage}
          alt="Personas disfrutando de una fiesta con una botella de tequila"
          quality="high"
          class="rounded-lg shadow-2xl shadow-secondary/20"
        />
      </div>

      <div
        class="w-11/12 md:w-1/2 lg:w-[35%]
        p-8 md:p-10
        bg-black/80 backdrop-blur-sm
        border border-secondary rounded-lg
        text-background
        relative -mt-24 lg:absolute lg:mt-0 lg:left-0 lg:top-1/2 lg:-translate-y-1/2"
      >
        <p class="font-body mt-4 text-lg text-background leading-relaxed">
          Cada gota de nuestro Volcanic es un tributo a la paciencia y la tradici칩n. Madurado en barricas de roble
          americano, este destilado absorbe la esencia de la tierra volc치nica, resultando en un sabor complejo y
          extraordinariamente suave.
        </p>

        <ul class="mt-6 space-y-3 font-body text-background">
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg
              class="w-5 h-5 mr-3 text-primary flex-shrink-0 mt-1"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              ><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg
            >
            <span><strong>Aroma:</strong> Notas de vainilla, caramelo y agave cocido.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg
              class="w-5 h-5 mr-3 text-primary flex-shrink-0 mt-1"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              ><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg
            >
            <span><strong>Sabor:</strong> Equilibrio perfecto entre roble tostado y frutos secos.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg
              class="w-5 h-5 mr-3 text-primary flex-shrink-0 mt-1"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              ><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg
            >
            <span><strong>Acabado:</strong> Largo, c치lido y persistentemente suave.</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
